headline: CCL's Fuel & FX Tailwinds Build in 2026: How Material Is the Cushion?
summary: Carnival sees a $0.20 EPS boost in FY26 from fuel and FX tailwinds, but rising costs and regulatory hits may offset part of the cushion.
